{"tid":153693,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"啱啱真係差少少就死咗⋯⋯","createTime":"2017-03-12T17:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-14T03:47:19.000Z","uid":67389,"like":187,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"043f660cf57a524ec1d6fee3198adec75a8cbc73","tid":153693,"uid":67389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:40:47.000Z","msg":"今晚同朋友食完飯敍完舊之後，<br />\n我就自己一個去搭的士，<br />\n啱啱諗住行過條馬路到個的士站嗰陣，<br />\n轉角位突然有架波子衝緊埋嚟，<br />\n嗰個距離我真係閃都閃唔切，<br />\n個腦一片空白，靜到聽到心跳聲卜卜聲，<br />\n好彩個司機剎得切我先無事，<br />\n我仲成個人嚇到跌咗落地望住佢個車頭燈<br />\n<br />\n上到的士冷靜完之後就喺到諗，<br />\n如果啱啱真係死咗會點，<br />\n又諗起屋企兩老，諗起啲啱啱先敍完舊嘅朋友，<br />\n如果死咗嘅就以後都再見唔到佢地<br />\n<br />\n成日睇新聞見到好多人自殺，有時我會諗，<br />\n可能死咗得到解脫，唔係一件壞事，<br />\n但當真係面對過死亡嘅時候，<br />\n先會發現原來自己並唔係真係咁諗<br />\n<br />\n好多事覺得死咗會得到解脫，<br />\n咁係因為你仲未搵到一樣你值得為佢而生存嘅嘢，<br />\n不論係事定人，但當你一搵到嘅時候，<br />\n請你唔好咁輕易就放棄"},{"pid":"044d2aa769bca5ec31ffd776dc71910e56bb4f61","tid":153693,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:42:52.000Z","msg":"有無玩緊電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c2361a8c524071b90341a8c2a0cb0ea9f8242d9","tid":153693,"uid":1436,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:43:15.000Z","msg":"咁個司機有冇屌鳩你想死行遠啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  btw過馬路要小心"},{"pid":"79015235bbe6b8364334b27a86dc2735beab0619","tid":153693,"uid":19725,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:43:45.000Z","msg":"我係法國一樣 <br />\n趕搭飛機 <br />\n差一步就比貨櫃車撞到 架車 同我個鼻差幾cm 經過 <br />\n痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4774f58f40ca708c4abec27a42634d9904c4eaa5","tid":153693,"uid":67389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:44:33.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有無玩緊電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n無呀本身個位真係睇唔到有車出我先行"},{"pid":"18d2e7853775b9a9731e0993bfc159da3eef02be","tid":153693,"uid":49353,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:44:52.000Z","msg":"巴打真係死過翻生<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n當人生去到盡頭就會浮現自己最需要嘅嘢<br />\n珍惜吧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/like.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19de447532bdd56673f22e015d0739e550538125","tid":153693,"uid":75694,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:45:09.000Z","msg":"以為樓主學kobe咁跳過架車"},{"pid":"4eda8fa9741b2b63141e4854d85475e9513d45f2","tid":153693,"uid":67389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:45:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>咁個司機有冇屌鳩你想死行遠啲<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/26.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  btw過馬路要小心</blockquote><br />\n無喎，我起返身之後佢就走咗，<br />\n乜都無講<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c5a328aa730308540ae870dc1dd7a38ec3fc9633","tid":153693,"uid":50456,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T17:48:54.000Z","msg":"試過係中央出面等過馬路<br />\n有架的士衝左上行人路<br />\n果刻完全反應唔到 呆左望住佢向自己衝埋黎<br />\n好在係佢岩岩好停正係我面前<br />\n嚇到唔記得屌個司機就走左<br />\n即刻打電話比老豆講講下忍唔住係條街喊出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9cb42475d27f53dc7dfaaa0c3dfd097b5f9c0f67","tid":153693,"uid":36026,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T18:33:58.000Z","msg":"撞得死都算好彩<br />\n撞唔死變植物人就慘"},{"pid":"093bc515f6d5d710809d110e1f7365f1c1408531","tid":153693,"uid":87860,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T18:37:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8796b59f5f8ab6e2798155371fdf882b3b5bb0bf","tid":153693,"uid":4672,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T18:37:36.000Z","msg":"俾車撞唔一定會死<br />\n<br />\n個標題應該改成 差少少俾車撞"},{"pid":"b798c94b18c0da795c13b33955cdbe64c10af206","tid":153693,"uid":9339,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T18:43:57.000Z","msg":"講起俾車撞<br />\n之前我過馬路果陣明明係綠色公仔<br />\n有一隻腳已經踏左出去<br />\n屌你老母有架車仲要繼續行過黎<br />\n差d就俾佢車撚扁我隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為我睇錯交通燈啦<br />\n屌！原來架車真係衝左紅燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a5f5fcec15756e42ab6cd660b5eb3de853dc746","tid":153693,"uid":15921,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T18:48:22.000Z","msg":"求下你唔好亂過馬路累人啦"},{"pid":"000df3efe867bbf105e85df1bb64d647eee3564b","tid":153693,"uid":43308,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T18:51:21.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"9d67c9855307229a32f03f9a2c440321da68a421","tid":153693,"uid":3779,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T18:59:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>講起俾車撞<br />\n之前我過馬路果陣明明係綠色公仔<br />\n有一隻腳已經踏左出去<br />\n屌你老母有架車仲要繼續行過黎<br />\n差d就俾佢車撚扁我隻腳<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我以為我睇錯交通燈啦<br />\n屌！原來架車真係衝左紅燈<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我之前都試過，係仆街的士佬<br />\n個縱刻又係個腦空白哂，但隻腳自動識踏返後<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1bd5c023cfb5e1e877c2f63676f09d77f753440e","tid":153693,"uid":55789,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T19:06:36.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>撞得死都算好彩<br />\n撞唔死變植物人就慘</blockquote><br />\n植物人都唔慘<br />\n無左手手腳腳仲慘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"de663c6acff884e1515b5f5a060e640df194c0fd","tid":153693,"uid":75326,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T19:06:54.000Z","msg":"呢個情況一定係你人生轉捩點，等你以後好好計劃每一步!<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3b2db74fe17b1e9dc4a74ff65393d99d121e4358","tid":153693,"uid":26053,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-12T19:16:00.000Z","msg":"好耐之前差啲比架綿羊仔撞<br />\n又試過上面跌野落黎差兩步我就係個個位"},{"pid":"aee